the asshole who did them.

05:51.308 --> 05:54.103
This man's whole life
is about killing.

05:54.186 --> 05:56.855
He studies it.
He knows forensics.

05:56.939 --> 05:58.899
He understands
police procedure.

05:58.941 --> 06:02.778
He prepares methodically so as to not 
to leave any evidence at the scene.

06:05.739 --> 06:10.369
After he picks his target,
he'll watch her for weeks.

06:10.452 --> 06:13.122
He'll study every detail
of her routine--

06:13.205 --> 06:16.917
When she comes home.
When she goes to sleep.

06:20.170 --> 06:23.549
In the morning
before the sun comes up,

06:23.632 --> 06:26.844
