walk around half-naked seven hours later.

06:34.810 --> 06:37.104
Finally,
he'll pick a day.

06:38.355 --> 06:40.858
Takes a kit of tools and props--

06:40.941 --> 06:45.112
duct tape, handcuffs, a weapon--
whatever he needs.

06:45.195 --> 06:47.114
He'll let himself in.

06:49.283 --> 06:51.201
That night,
she'll get home.

06:51.285 --> 06:54.246
Go about her business,
unaware that he's in the house.

07:46.590 --> 07:50.511
Oh... this is good.

07:59.228 --> 08:01.355
Shall we dance ? 

08:01.438 --> 08:05.150
No, don't play hard to get.

08:05.234 --> 08:07.152
This will be fun.

08:16.620 --> 08:19.248
Shh.

08:19.331 --> 08:24.003
Shh. It's over.
It's all right.

08:24.086 --> 08:26.213
Shh. 

