Why did you turn
away from me ?

11:42.826 --> 11:46.121
Why was it so hard
for you to accept ?

11:46.163 --> 11:49.249
'Cause you know
I did it for you.

11:50.334 --> 11:53.545
You came so close to me
that night.

11:53.629 --> 11:56.757
I remember clearly what I felt
when I heard your footsteps following behind me.

11:56.840 --> 12:00.052
- Pride.

12:02.137 --> 12:04.515
