Yeah, chief of Chicago P.D.
already called.

20:50.791 --> 20:53.335
Not surprising,
I suppose, they're inviting us in on this.

20:53.419 --> 20:56.005
They're setting up a joint task force
as we speak.

20:56.088 --> 20:59.967
I'd like to know if you think
you can handle it on our end.

21:00.009 --> 21:01.885
I know that in L.A.--

21:01.969 --> 21:04.430
Oh, no, this isn't L.A.
It's not my job anymore.

21:04.513 --> 21:07.766
You know what ? The only reason 
that your burnt-out, messed-up ass...

21:07.808 --> 21:10.853
