you had a three-year head start on us.

21:10.936 --> 21:16.275
This perp is set on putting you
in the middle of this shit whether we like it or not.

21:16.316 --> 21:20.070
You're right.
The field office in L.A. has the relevant files.

21:20.154 --> 21:22.072
I can't tell you anything
that's not in them.

21:24.700 --> 21:26.660
I'm sorry.

21:27.995 --> 21:29.955
Mike. Excuse me.

21:29.997 --> 21:33.834
Mike, we got several sets of prints
