23:39.251 --> 23:41.170
Okay.

23:42.254 --> 23:44.298
Let's talk about that.

23:46.467 --> 23:49.803
I go places,
and I forget why I'm there.

23:49.887 --> 23:51.930
I miss exits on the freeway.

23:53.891 --> 23:57.227
I'm lucky to...
find my way home from the grocery store.

23:57.311 --> 24:00.564
And if I do, then...

24:00.647 --> 24:03.359
most of the time
I've forgotten my groceries.

24:04.943 --> 24:07.571
But yet, you make it
here every week.

24:08.655 --> 24:10.574
Twice a week.

24:18.582 --> 24:20.542
Yeah.

24:20.584 --> 24:23.420
You do.

24:26.006 --> 24:29.385
What if the next picture
that arrived was of your daughter ?

24:30.761 --> 24:33.931
Would you really want me
to be the one looking for her ?

24:37.643 --> 24:39.812
Yes.

24:42.356 --> 24:46.568
Yes... I would.

24:46.652 --> 24:49.780
From this moment

24:49.947 --> 24:52.574
How can it feel

24:52.658 --> 24:54.576
This wrong

25:46.378 --> 25:48.839
Hello.
Hi. It's me.

25:48.922 --> 25:50.841
Me ?

25:56.138 --> 25:58.057
Me who ?

25:58.140 --> 26:01.810
It's freaking cold here.
Why'd you move here ?

26:06.231 --> 26:08.150
What the fuck
do you want from me ?

26:08.233 --> 26:11.278
