but then I thought, "Chicago's not so bad."

26:31.882 --> 26:34.593
At least you didn't move
to New Jersey, right ?

26:34.677 --> 26:36.595
Yeah.

26:37.763 --> 26:39.682
So, why don't you
grab a pen ?

26:39.765 --> 26:42.976
I'll give you the name and number of the...
agent that's on your case.

26:43.060 --> 26:47.815
You can... share your inner turmoil with him
'cause I don't give a shit.

26:47.898 --> 26:50.901
I know your job
is hard, Joel,

26:50.984 --> 26:54.947
