Who is it ?
 Flowers for Joel Campbell.

28:21.742 --> 28:24.953
You didn't answer the phone. The door downstairs was open,
so I thought I'd just bring--

28:27.998 --> 28:29.958
Put the flowers on the floor.

28:32.294 --> 28:34.213
Thank you.

28:42.179 --> 28:44.973
The photos, Joel.

28:45.057 --> 28:50.104
I'll send you a picture,
