28:58.487 --> 29:01.365
What if the next picture that arrived
was of your daughter?

29:01.448 --> 29:03.992
Really want me to be the one
looking for her?

29:04.076 --> 29:06.412
Yes.
I'll send you a picture.

29:06.495 --> 29:08.747
You can have a day
to try to find her.

29:12.543 --> 29:15.004
