on this Kodak paper. You got it.

29:48.454 --> 29:50.372
Is that mine ?
Thanks.

29:50.456 --> 29:53.500
I'm sorry. I can't remember your name.
Mitch Casper.

29:53.584 --> 29:55.711
Mitch, get this in the computer
and blow it up.

29:55.794 --> 29:58.505
Find out what's behind her on the wall.
That thing right there.

29:58.589 --> 30:01.342
Find out what kind of earrings she's wearing,
what kind of blouse that is.

30:01.383 --> 30:04.178
- What's that on her glasses ?
- Reflection, yeah.

30:04.261 --> 30:06.472
Find out something
about her. Anything.

30:06.555 --> 30:09.099
Both girls are basically loners,
very little social contact.

30:09.183 --> 30:11.518
The last girl's parents
were deceased.

30:11.602 --> 30:15.147
No close friends as far as we can tell.
Is that his victim profile ?

30:15.230 --> 30:18.484
No. I mean, the victims
were always young women,

30:18.567 --> 30:20.486
but he's sending
pictures now.

30:20.569 --> 30:23.113
He's only gonna target loners.
You know, women people don't notice.

30:23.197 --> 30:25.574
