a picture of the prom queen.

30:25.657 --> 30:28.077
Yeah. Well, listen.
Before we go any further,

30:28.160 --> 30:31.205
we're gonna have to make a decision
as to whether to go to the press with this.

30:31.288 --> 30:33.415
We gotta make it now.

30:33.499 --> 30:37.670
Look. There's no decision to make. 
