this woman's life is in serious danger.

30:49.139 --> 30:53.477
The Chicago Police Department
and the F.B.I. are working in concert...

30:53.519 --> 30:56.605
to try and locate her,
and we're gonna be grateful for any help...

30:56.647 --> 30:58.691
you guys can give us
in this endeavor.

30:58.774 --> 31:02.569
Every hour is critical.
That's all.

31:05.280 --> 31:07.199
This young woman is missing.

31:07.282 --> 31:11.286
Authorities are frantically searching for her.
They fear for her safety.

31:11.370 --> 31:14.123
Any information on the whereabouts
or the identity of the woman...

31:14.206 --> 31:17.459
police are referring to as "Jane Doe,
"please call the number on your screen.

31:17.543 --> 31:19.753
This is the photograph
of an unknown young woman...

31:19.837 --> 31:23.549
who they say might fall victim to a murder
if she is not located by 9.:00.

31:23.632 --> 31:27.928
"What kind of earrings are those ?
What kind of blouse is that ?"

31:28.012 --> 31:30.889
What are you bitching about ?
Oh, come on, Diana.

31:30.973 --> 31:35.978
