how well he knows this creep.

31:38.188 --> 31:41.650
I say if his pupils don't dilate,
then we don't need him.

31:43.235 --> 31:46.321
Ma'am, there-- There hasn't
been a reward established,

31:46.405 --> 31:48.365
but I'm sure something can be done.

31:51.410 --> 31:53.412
Okay. Today ?
Was that today ?

31:53.495 --> 31:56.165
Okay, thank you.
